- [ ] 6. Add `source` lines and remove duplicated boilerplate in `skills/npm-agent/scripts/npm-agent.sh` using the same `setup_outdir`/`setup_lock` pattern and retaining npm-specific helpers and commands.
- [ ] 7. Add `source` lines and remove duplicated boilerplate in `skills/terra-agent/scripts/terra-agent.sh` using the same `setup_outdir`/`setup_lock` pattern and preserving terraform command flow.
